description:
A mail analyzing application which helps you to reduce time, effort and cost for your daily mail sorting.

Netpas MMA is mail analyzing application which helps you to reduce time, effort and cost for your daily mail sorting.
Netpas MMA analyzes tens of thousands mails and creates your database. You can make searching, filtering and matching cargos and vessels. Save time, effort and cost with Netpas MMA. Don't worry. All mails and analyzed cards are saved in your local PC only.
